---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="How to Switch Payroll Providers — Pink Payroll">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-5">Zero-Friction Transition</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6 max-w-4xl">
        Think Switching is a Headache?<br class="hidden md:block" />
        <span class="text-pink">We've Turned it Into a Science.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Most business owners stay with a payroll company they hate because they fear the transition. We've perfected a "Zero-Friction" process that gets you moved, audited, and live — without you lifting a finger.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== 4-STEP TIMELINE ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Process</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black">The 4-Step "White-Glove" Transition</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <ol class="relative">

      <!-- Connecting line -->
      <div class="absolute left-6 top-6 bottom-6 w-0.5 bg-brand-light-gray" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <li class="relative flex gap-8 pb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold text-lg shadow-lg z-10">
          1
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1.5 flex-1">
          <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Step One</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">The Fast-Track Intake</h3>
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              We start with a simple digital intake. Once you sign the service agreement and provide a voided check, our team immediately goes to work securing your new account. <strong class="text-brand-black">No long forms, no redundant data.</strong>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <li class="relative flex gap-8 pb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold text-lg shadow-lg z-10">
          2
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1.5 flex-1">
          <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Step Two</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">The Precision Profile</h3>
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Accuracy is our obsession. We'll have a brief, high-level conversation or a streamlined survey to map out your pay frequencies, sick/vacation accruals, and unique business rules. <strong class="text-brand-black">We build your system to fit your business, not the other way around.</strong>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <li class="relative flex gap-8 pb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold text-lg shadow-lg z-10">
          3
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1.5 flex-1">
          <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Step Three</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">The "Done-For-You" Data Migration</h3>
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Send us your last few reports — or better yet, <strong class="text-brand-black">grant us access to your old provider and we'll gather the data ourselves.</strong> Our team manually builds your history and audits every year-to-date total to ensure your tax history is flawless.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <li class="relative flex gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold text-lg shadow-lg z-10">
          4
        </div>
        <div class="pt-1.5 flex-1">
          <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Step Four</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-3">The Parallel Run <span class="text-brand-gray font-semibold text-base">(The Safety Net)</span></h3>
          <div class="bg-pink/5 border border-pink/30 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
              Before your first "live" pay date, we run a practice payroll in the background. We verify that every penny matches your previous records. <strong class="text-brand-black">This ensures that on your first real payday with Pink Payroll, everything is 100% perfect.</strong>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>

    </ol>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WHITE GLOVE PROMISE ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-gray/40 border-y border-brand-light-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Our Promise</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We Handle the Heavy Lifting.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        From coordinating the "final goodbye" to your old provider to verifying your historical tax filings, we manage the entire transition.
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-black font-semibold text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your employees get paid on time, your tax records stay clean, and you finally get a partner who actually answers the phone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FINAL CTA ===== -->
  <section class="bg-pink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Ready for a Fresh Start?</h2>
      <p class="text-pink-light text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Stop tolerating "okay" payroll. Let our experts handle the move for you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/client-set-up" class="bg-white text-pink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-base">
          Start Your Switch Today
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white/60 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-base">
          Talk to an Onboarding Specialist
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
